▒▒▒░▐      It's hard to think of words to describe the James Bond          ▌░▒▒▒
▒▒░░▌      Ultimate Edition DVDs. Over a year ago we proudly released      ▐░░▒▒
▒░▄▀       the entire James Bond Special Edition DVD collection, but        ▀▄░▒
░▐         these new releases are a must have. After comparing the SE         ▌░
░▌         and UE DVDs it's like the difference between night and             ▐░
▐          day. It took DTS Digital Images two and a half years using          ▌
▐          600 PowerMac G5s and 700 TBs of storage to completely               ▌
▒▒▒░▐      remaster all of the movies. The company digitally removed       ▌░▒▒▒
▒▒░░▌      37 million pieces of dirt and 74,000 hairs in addition to       ▐░░▒▒
▒░▄▀       restoring the original colors. Even the oldest Bond movies       ▀▄░▒
░▐         now look as fresh as if they had been made this year.              ▌░
░▌         Additionally, the originaly soundtracks have been                  ▐░
▐          remastered making the audio richer with more detail.                ▌
